---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ArticleCTA from '../../components/ArticleCTA.astro';
import RelatedServices from '../../components/RelatedServices.astro';

const SITE = 'https://ltsmobilemechanics.com';
const slug = 'emergency-roadside';
const serviceTitle = 'Emergency Roadside';

const schemaData = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Service",
  "name": `Mobile ${serviceTitle} Service`,
  "description": `Professional mobile ${serviceTitle.toLowerCase()} service in Beaverton, Portland, and the greater Portland metro area. We come to you — Mon-Sat, 8am-7pm.`,
  "provider": {
    "@type": "LocalBusiness",
    "name": "LT's Mobile Mechanics",
    "telephone": "+19715340360",
    "url": SITE,
    "address": {
      "@type": "PostalAddress",
      "streetAddress": "4041 SW Hall Blvd",
      "addressLocality": "Beaverton",
      "addressRegion": "OR",
      "postalCode": "97005",
      "addressCountry": "US"
    }
  },
  "areaServed": [
    "Beaverton, OR","Portland, OR","Hillsboro, OR","Tigard, OR",
    "Lake Oswego, OR","Tualatin, OR","Aloha, OR","Gresham, OR"
  ],
  "url": `${SITE}/services/${slug}/`
};
---

<Layout
  title={`Mobile ${serviceTitle} in Beaverton & Portland, OR | LT's Mobile Mechanics`}
  description={`Mobile ${serviceTitle.toLowerCase()} service at your home or work in Beaverton, Portland, and the Portland metro. Professional, honest, and available Mon–Sat 8am–7pm. Call (971) 534-0360.`}
  keywords={`mobile ${serviceTitle.toLowerCase()} Portland, mobile mechanic ${serviceTitle.toLowerCase()}, ${serviceTitle.toLowerCase()} Beaverton, ${serviceTitle.toLowerCase()} Portland Oregon`}
  canonical={`https://ltsmobilemechanics.com/services/${slug}/`}
  schema={schemaData}
>
  <main>
    <section class="article-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Mobile Roadside Assistance in <em>Beaverton and Portland</em></h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">Broken down? Stranded during business hours? Fast mobile roadside assistance anywhere in the Portland metro, Mon–Sat 8am–7pm.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="container">
      <article class="article-body">
        <div class="article-content fade-up">
          <p>A vehicle breakdown can happen any day of the week. You could be sitting on the side of the freeway at rush hour, stuck in a parking lot in the rain, or stranded far from home with no idea what to do. That's when you need someone who can help fast. LTs Mobile Mechanics provides mobile roadside assistance throughout Beaverton, Portland, and the surrounding metro area, Monday through Saturday from 8 AM to 7 PM. When you're in trouble during business hours, Tristan will be there.</p>

          <h2>What Counts as an Emergency</h2>
          <p>Emergency situations come in all forms. Your car won't start and you're late for work. You got a flat tire on a dark road. Your engine overheated and you need help getting to safety. You ran out of gas. Your battery is dead. Your transmission died on the freeway. Your brakes are failing. Any of these can leave you feeling helpless, but they don't have to. Call LTs Mobile Mechanics and help is on the way.</p>

          <h2>We Get There Fast</h2>
          <p>When you call about a breakdown in Beaverton, Portland, or the surrounding areas during business hours, we prioritize your call. Tristan will get to you as quickly as possible. We keep you updated on his location and arrival time so you're not left wondering. Whether your breakdown is at 8 AM on a Monday or 6 PM on a Saturday, we treat it with the same urgency and professionalism.</p>

          <h2>What We Can Fix on the Spot</h2>
          <p>Many roadside emergencies can be fixed right where you broke down. Dead battery? We can jump start it. Blown fuse? We've got replacements. Hose or belt issue? We might be able to patch it. Flat tire? We can help get you to a tire shop or repair it. Engine overheating? We can assess the situation and advise on next steps. While some problems require towing, many can be resolved quickly so you can get back on the road.</p>

          <h2>Towing and Safe Alternatives</h2>
          <p>If your vehicle can't be fixed on the side of the road, we'll help coordinate towing or transport you somewhere safe. We have relationships with local tow companies and can arrange safe transport to a repair shop or your home. If you need just a ride to get somewhere while your vehicle is being fixed, we can help with that too. Our goal is to get you out of the emergency situation safely.</p>

          <h2>Flexible Hours, Everywhere</h2>
          <p>Here's what makes LTs Mobile Mechanics different for roadside help: we're mobile and we stay open longer than most shops. We stay open until 7 PM on weeknights, and we're open all day Saturday too. When your car breaks down during the week, call us. Tristan will come help you get the problem sorted, whether it's a quick fix or a bigger issue. Open Monday through Saturday, 8 AM to 7 PM throughout Beaverton, Portland, and the entire Portland metro area.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <ArticleCTA
      heading={`Ready for ${serviceTitle}?`}
      subheading={`Call LT's Mobile Mechanics. We come to you in Beaverton, Portland, and throughout the Portland metro — Mon–Sat, 8am–7pm.`}
    />

    <RelatedServices exclude={slug} />
  </main>
</Layout>
